plugin_metadata





/edge/admin/plugin_metadata/{id}

配置插件数据

请求方法
GET     /edge/admin/plugin_metadata/{plugin_name}                 根据 plugin_name 获取资源
PUT     /edge/admin/plugin_metadata/{plugin_name}         {body}  根据 plugin_name 创建资源
DELETE  /edge/admin/plugin_metadata/{plugin_name}                 删除资源


body 请求参数

json object 。根据各插件要求配置对应的数据属性


配置log_process的数据
curl -L -X PUT 'http://127.0.0.1:9990/edge/admin/plugin_metadata/log_process' -H 'X-API-KEY: f9357106bff442f89d4de7169c37c61e' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' --data-raw '{
    "logs": [
        {
            "formats": "${remote_addr},${host},${status}",
            "file": "logs/process.log"
        },
        {
            "formats": [
                "${remote_addr}",
                "${host}",
                "${status}"
            ],
            "file": "logs/other.log"
        }
    ]
}'

重新加载插件
curl -L -X PUT 'http://127.0.0.1:9990/edge/admin/plugins/reload' -H 'X-API-KEY: f9357106bff442f89d4de7169c37c61e'--data-raw ''


添加日志插件
curl -L -X PUT 'http://127.0.0.1:9990/edge/admin/routes/3001' -H 'X-API-KEY: f9357106bff442f89d4de7169c37c61e' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' --data-raw '{
    "uri": "/hello1/*",
    "plugins": {
        "log_process": {
          "files": "logs/process.log"
        }
    },
    "upstream": {
        "nodes": {
            "127.0.0.1:8111": 1
        },
        "type": "roundrobin"
    }
}'

测试请求
curl -L -X GET 'http://127.0.0.1:9980/hello1/h1?username=44dd&test=123a'


查看日志文件
logs/process.log



